Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想饿死我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我马上做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难吃 重做去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 去学校会迟到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管对这帮家伙怎样都无所谓么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我随时都能杀了它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.50,0:02:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}被束缚的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近经常看见那孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是刚搬来这附近的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她住在公园旁边的大公寓里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过据说她在下野太太家学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换每天去做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下野小姐能教书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人讨厌小孩的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过下野太太以前是学校的老师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承了家人的财产后马上就辞职了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她家人知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像来打过一次招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过下野太太表面文章做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成被骗了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父母都上班到很晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想找个人看着孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你学校的老师来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然没把他放在眼里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的和谁都没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早说过你说了会怎么样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什么也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了可以随时杀死它们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连坟墓都不能好好给你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶还没好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这搞笑艺人真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 时间已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.10,0:05:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去后要好好学习啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是你的家庭教师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你成绩下降了被怀疑的可是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinky
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.90,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那时我没松手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她居然会真的下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 迟早Pinki也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让那家伙下地狱去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会为你报仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美纪 还没睡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki和Pinki还没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 还是放弃算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再稍微找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.70,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早餐已经做好了 要好好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.40,0:08:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 喂 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又看见了吧 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稻草人已经给了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.80,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 有没有能判断地点的标记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的建筑或者 商店名字什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有人要被送去地狱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.90,0:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要阻止吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.00,0:09:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好找的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是母亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下野太太 她是一个人生活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.40,0:10:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承了家人的大笔财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不工作就呆在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的时候好像也和很多人交往过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没听说她结婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞错人家了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那孩子的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近出入下野家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前经带狗散步的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从公园旁边的公寓过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为Yuki没有了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.50,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们该不会想一起逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这脚是因为谁的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敢逃走我决不饶你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我随时都可以弄死它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也随时都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那起过了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点动静也没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到底在想什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道一定很无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不见得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.50,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子每天都对着我说着同样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也随时都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给 这就是您委托的调查结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, 谢谢了 帮了大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上川美纪 初中一年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近身边没有突然死亡或者失踪的人 啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃复仇了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗倒是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.30,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有狗失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从搬到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晚带狗散步成了她的日常习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在学校并不出众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有要好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父母都因为工作常常不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有两条狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是她的知心朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是两个星期前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散步途中狗就失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好从那时起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就开始出入这间房子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这之间应该有联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢对人说我就把狗杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近有个可疑的男人经常出没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你说出去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我不知道那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是没遵守约定的你不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上把它杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这帮家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当妈妈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.50,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了这狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinki Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快给我做早饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.10,0:15:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该不会是想饿死我再夺走我的财产吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是想换换心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变了散步的路线而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼 疼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开 喂 好疼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的狗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的院子弄得一团糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还咬伤我的腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要给我负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为听说咬人狗会被处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才一直唯命是从
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉Yuki和Pinki就好像变成了人质似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问了老师说根本就没有这会事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有被处理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有病的狗之类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这样我一开始和妈妈商量就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然妈妈说不喜欢狗 商量一下的话一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你去商量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.20,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢说的话 这次是这群家伙一只只死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样的话 Pinki就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给 换的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一好臭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好几天没洗澡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么臭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不能不盯着那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个样子 大概可以放心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女做的事情是坏事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺走他人的生命的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么理由也不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是世上有人做了更坏的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也若无其事的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人又由谁来惩罚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那和这个不是一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是车站附近的驻警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然你那个时候看见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 我什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.00,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上川 喂上川 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的学生在里面惨叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.60,0:19:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请求支援 地点是柴田街八号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点 小家伙们就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也在打我财产的主意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.00,0:19:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.90,0:19:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人杀死了我养的Yuki和Pinki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会交给任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我会控告你妨碍警务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 我不会给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.10,0:19:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一分钱也不会给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 放开我 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.80,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来她以为女孩看见了她孩子的尸骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便把财产给孩子也不愿意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是地狱少女给你的人偶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.50,0:20:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说已经没用了 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些小家伙们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些小家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才刚刚出生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连名字都还没取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是早点把那人送下地狱就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明随时都可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了父母才好不容易得到的财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能交给小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就杀了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.30,0:21:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是狗还是什么我都要杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过即使习惯杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被杀还是头一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.90,0:21:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤害 鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.80,0:21:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.80,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是去什么地狱的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不赶快回去财产就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.20,0:22:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己是什么样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.50,0:22:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.40,0:22:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.00,0:22:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再早点解开绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinki就不会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗们也都不会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.10,0:22:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时… 明明随时可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.70,0:22:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
